## Code Rules

1. Import from `@e-burgos/tucu-ui` only
2. Use `LucideIcons` from tucu-ui, NOT `lucide-react`
3. Use `CardContainer` over `<div>` for themed containers
4. Use semantic tokens (`bg-primary`) not static colors (`bg-blue-500`)
5. Use `Form` + `validationSchema`, not raw react-hook-form
6. Use tucu-ui routing system, not raw react-router-dom
